{"tid":1903588,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"香港人好唔好再登報？#hongkongerstandwithyou","createTime":"2020-02-29T05:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T17:05:25.000Z","uid":144533,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9841c61283eaee4ebacacf6f3e9393384d7c1726","tid":1903588,"uid":144533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"話說上一個Po講我希望借武肺等外國人意識到HK is not Chi Na<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全世界更激烈嘅排華意識開始爆發，香港人點算？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902932</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實學巴打話齋，外國人點會分別到香港人同中國人，所以我唔在乎佢哋區唔區分得到，預咗攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我只希望更多外國人知道香港人係唔同嘅，而我亦相信好好好好好好多外國人係唔知。<br />\n<br />\n而我認為今次係一個好機會，俾香港人做次主動，支持返佢哋抗疫，令香港越出名，對我哋越有利。<br />\n<br />\n根據巴絲打提議，可以整嗰抗疫指南，話我哋有沙士經驗，有d就話登報。所以想問下大家同唔同意再登報，集思廣益吓，有咩可以改，俾文宣組做野。"},{"pid":"d8dfbc897c82487e71ccc6c78df06cf40e13f765","tid":1903588,"uid":144533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T05:11:30.000Z","msg":"小弟才疏學淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，想開放討論同歡迎修改，屌細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇上次登報結果，有d報章會同原本design有出入，所以我認為可以定咗必要嘅野先。<br />\n以下係個人意見，有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三大重點：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 防疫資訊</span></span><br />\n  a. 唔好太盡信世衞，佢同中國有利關係，唔好睇武肺<br />\n  b. 預防勝於治療，帶口罩勤清潔消毒<br />\n  c. 有潛伏期，冇唔舒服唔代表冇嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. #hongkongerstandwithyou</span></span><br />\n  a. 係Hongkonger唔係Hong Kong(避免誤會同HKG有關)<br />\n  b. 香港仲抗爭緊，多謝一直以來嘅關心，今次抗疫我哋都會支持返你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. #HKisnotChiNa</span></span><br />\n  a. 記得沙士嗎？當時都係大陸傳落嚟，我哋有防疫經驗，當然會支持返你哋<br />\n<br />\n*表達正面，避用racist字眼圖案*<br />\n<br />\n另外登報嘅同時，可以spread開poster, GIF, video版本</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5f2a4f03cbd1fb272b0ce87e37b6eca3484e69a3","tid":1903588,"uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"覺得可行性不大, 但幫你推推"},{"pid":"9243eddf7673761c64f2234eadd393a7d6d25c9a","tid":1903588,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T08:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係要搵啲專家出嚟會好啲<br />\n畢竟有應對沙士經驗唔等於專家"},{"pid":"156aa9e51165b6e338c0f5229593d0f9e2b4bb5e","tid":1903588,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f2a4f03cbd1fb272b0ce87e37b6eca3484e69a3","tid":1903588,"uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"覺得可行性不大, 但幫你推推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T09:05:21.000Z","msg":"之前登報個效果都係吹大左<br />\nG20根本唔係想像中咁重要<br />\n當時有班end game 撚係咁吹風先成到事<br />\n但呢d怪風都好影響抗爭陣營既情緒 下下end game 但每次都輸 <br />\n之後既行動係黑驚同港共自己做柒野 先搞得番起"},{"pid":"96b4ed48ac1641c366fbbcf9108cd69d6afb02f2","tid":1903588,"uid":350576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"推 登報講武肺幾危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多外國人唔知 講俾佢地聽中國同WHO 啲衰野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0502895ea528916b85b48140248f297d83be5996","tid":1903588,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96b4ed48ac1641c366fbbcf9108cd69d6afb02f2","tid":1903588,"uid":350576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"推 登報講武肺幾危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多外國人唔知 講俾佢地聽中國同WHO 啲衰野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"同埋拎我地sars個時點教個人防疫翻譯做英文，等多d人分開中國同香港，唔好打得係外國既香港人咁甘"},{"pid":"73eac8a7ecffe68e7b8b14f32e70d726e3041faf","tid":1903588,"uid":216521,"like":0,"dislike":